<p>Hi, we’re EVEN<sup>®</sup> Hotels and we know that many travelers, like you, wish there were more options to stay healthier and happier away from home. That’s why we’re here with a wellness-savvy staff, a best-in-class fitness experience, healthier food choices and natural, relaxing spaces.<br>
<br>
This way to a better stay.</p>
